asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

Did I tell you I am really humble? I just remembered, Ive probably got genetics from cupid, thats why Im so good with my arrow, and the fluffies. Like my gold necklace? Hold on, did you hear a scream? I have to go and save some fluff! Again. . .

name: Pepper
description: Born and raised in a quiet, humble community, Peppers lifestyle is simple. Well, in her words actually, it is boring. Mundane. Cautious. It is no fault of her family that caution is of the utmost importance, of course, considering her father survived the Winston Raid way back when. Her fathers warnings were ever present at the dinner table. NEVER approach those tunnels, Pepper. DO YOU HEAR ME! You never kn, know what is lurking in the tunnels. Yep, I got it, dad. Loud and clear. I know. And since Pepper carries the family lineage through a dignified Darkness Fur and those signature, hypnotic Purple Ring eyes, she is never beyond the sight of a watchful sibling or family friend. She feels trapped. You see, Pepper has always been an outlier. An exception. An anomaly. She has always felt different. Her siblings abide by the creed but she just does not get it. Why must I stay here? Why am I not allowed to go somewhere else? Flufs are curious by NATURE. MOM. UGH. She cannot explain it but Pepper has always yearned for something more. And that yearning is starting to bubble up. Something is happening. Pepper is beginning to awaken. There is a deep calling rising up inside of her. A burning desire to escape and explore and experience the Underground for all that it has to offer. Peppers journey is just beginning. Are you prepared for what comes next?
